title: Skins Seasons 1 and 2
description:
The complete first and second series (seasons) of the British teen drama Skins. I did not rip the individual episodes, I downloaded them. Thanks to RiVER for uploading most of the episodes that I downloaded.


"Skins revolves around the lives of a group of 16 - 19 year-old friends who live in Bristol. The Dawson Brothers claim the series represents the everyday lives of adolescents. The group includes: a popular boy (Tony), a Muslim boy (Anwar), an openly gay boy (Maxxie), an intelligent and privileged girl with family problems (Jal), a party animal in love with his teacher (Chris), a pushover who is in love with his best friend\&#039;s girlfriend (Sid), a girl who is worried about her boyfriend\&#039;s feelings for her (Michelle), and a girl with an eating disorder (Cassie). These characters attend the fictional Roundview Sixth Form College in Bristol. Each instalment has a self-contained theme focusing on each different character respectively, but there are several story arcs that span different episodes."
